eclasstool.model.drawingtools

Class Text

  • java.lang.Object
    • eclasstool.model.drawingtools.Shape
      • eclasstool.model.drawingtools.Text

  • public class Text
extends Shape
    Text is the implementation of the text tool for the E-classroom for use directly on the lecture slide's canvas.
